OL,3,CCould rare Sting Jet bring 'danger to
OL,4,Clife' winds this weekend?
OL,6,FAs eyes turn to the Atlantic, experts
OL,7,Fare increasingly concerned that a
OL,8,F'sting jet' will develop within Storm
OL,9,FDave and bring dangerous winds across
OL,10,Fparts of the UK.
OL,12,FWhat is a Sting Jet?
OL,14,FA sting jet is a narrow band of very
OL,15,Fstrong winds which briefly develops
OL,16,Fnear the centre of a storm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
