OL,3,CCould rare Sting Jet bring 'danger to
OL,4,Clife' winds this weekend?
OL,6,FThe area is usually small, up to 30
OL,7,Fmiles across. It is called a sting jet
OL,8,Fbecause it appears as a curl of cloud
OL,9,Faround the centre of a storm on
OL,10,Fsatellite imagery, giving the
OL,11,Fappearance of a scorpion's tail.
OL,13,FHow common are they?
OL,15,FRoughly one in every three storms to
OL,16,Fhit the UK see a sting jet develop so,
OL,17,Fthey are definitely an unusual
OL,18,Fphenomenon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
