OL,3,CCould rare Sting Jet bring 'danger to
OL,4,Clife' winds this weekend?
OL,6,FSome of the most memorable have been
OL,7,Fin Storm Eowyn in January 2025 which
OL,8,Fbrought gusts of 114mph to Mace Head
OL,9,Fin the Republic of Ireland and also
OL,10,FThe Great Storm of 1987 which brought
OL,11,Fgusts of 115mph.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FWhy do they form?
OL,26,@oD@Jqb
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
