PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775311858
OL,3,CCould rare Sting Jet bring 'danger to
OL,4,Clife' winds this weekend?
OL,6,FA sting jet forms in rapidly deepening
OL,7,Flow pressure (storm) systems, as air
OL,8,Ffrom high in the atmosphere descends
OL,9,Fquickly.
OL,11,FSnow and rain falling through that
OL,12,Fdescending air causes the air to cool
OL,13,Feven further which, in turn,
OL,14,Faccelerates the winds to higher speeds.
OL,16,FHow likely is it with Storm Dave?
OL,18,FThere is a potential for a sting jet
OL,19,Fto form with Storm Dave, most likely
OL,20,Fnear Northern Ireland, during Saturday
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
