OL,3,CCould rare Sting Jet bring 'danger to
OL,4,Clife' winds this weekend?
OL,6,FEven without the development of a
OL,7,Fsting jet, there is still potential
OL,8,Ffor gusts of 80mph around the coasts
OL,9,Fin the northwest of England overnight
OL,10,Fduring Storm Dave, and up to 90mph
OL,11,Faround Scottish coasts.
OL,13,FAre further weather warnings expected?
OL,15,FIt is very possible that the Met
OL,16,FOffice will decide to escalate or
OL,17,Fexpand some warning areas in the next
OL,18,F24 hours.
OL,20,FYou are strongly advised to keep up to
OL,21,Fdate with this developing situation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
